<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.1">
<l>vāraṇa māyirañ cūḻava lañceytu</l>
<l>nāraṇa ṉampi naṭakkiṉṟā ṉeṉṟetir</l>
<l>pūraṇa poṟkuṭam vaittup purameṅkum</l>
<l>tōraṇa nāṭṭak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that festoons were set up everywhere in the town</l>
<l>With golden pots filled [with water] being placed before</l>
<l>because the great Nārāyaṇa was walking rightwards [towards here]</l>
<l>as a thousand elephants surround [Him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
